<%- include('../partials/head') %>
<section class="guide-hero-v35">
  <p class="eyebrow">Seller Guide</p>
  <h1>How to present a used wall printer professionally.</h1>
  <p>A complete listing helps serious buyers understand the machine faster and reduces repetitive questions during the introduction process.</p>
</section>

<section class="guide-steps-v35">
  <article>
    <span>1</span>
    <h2>Prepare machine information</h2>
    <p>Include brand, model, production year, purchase year, printhead type, printhead count, working status, known defects, included accessories, and asking price.</p>
  </article>
  <article>
    <span>2</span>
    <h2>Upload useful media</h2>
    <p>Show the full machine, rails, printheads, ink system, control box, software screen, nameplate, accessories, and recent print samples. Clear photos reduce buyer uncertainty.</p>
  </article>
  <article>
    <span>3</span>
    <h2>Explain condition honestly</h2>
    <p>Describe what works, what does not work, maintenance history, storage condition, repairs, and anything the buyer should know before arranging inspection or shipping.</p>
  </article>
  <article>
    <span>4</span>
    <h2>Keep contact details private</h2>
    <p>Your direct contact details and exact address are not publicly displayed. They may be shared with qualified buyers after admin review.</p>
  </article>
</section>

<section class="guide-cta-v35">
  <div>
    <h2>Ready to submit a machine?</h2>
    <p>Use the floating Sell button on the homepage and complete the seller declaration before submitting.</p>
  </div>
  <a class="btn primary" href="/">Go to machines</a>
</section>
<%- include('../partials/foot') %>
